Updated logic to recognize both 'internet' and 'internet-trial' package types when selecting customer subscriptions and processing router services. Ensured correct filtering in product list handling.

refactor(auth): simplify login flow and email uniqueness check
Refactored authentication logic to streamline login verification by consolidating admin, customer, and employee email checks. Removed redundant conditions for customer login using customerId or email.
Updated email uniqueness validation across admin, customer, and employee to ensure no duplicate entries across roles.
These changes improve code readability, maintainability, and performance.
